      "> **Key Takeaways:** Germany (DACH) requires higher trust signals (Impressum/GDPR) than most markets. Local SEO is dominant via GBP and specific German directories. AI Overviews are shifting click patterns, requiring highly structured, authoritative content to maintain visibility.",
